✅ SEN QILA OLADIGAN YECHIM

👉 Dynamic App Icon (Android alias orqali)

Bu professional usul.

🔥 1. ANDROID SETUP

AndroidManifest.xml ga qo‘sh:

<activity-alias
    android:name=".MainActivityBlue"
    android:enabled="true"
    android:exported="true"
    android:icon="@mipmap/ic_launcher_blue"
    android:targetActivity=".MainActivity">

    <intent-filter>
        <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN"/>
        <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER"/>
    </intent-filter>

</activity-alias>

<activity-alias
    android:name=".MainActivityDark"
    android:enabled="false"
    android:exported="true"
    android:icon="@mipmap/ic_launcher_dark"
    android:targetActivity=".MainActivity"/>
🔥 2. FLUTTER PACKAGE
android_dynamic_icon: ^0.0.5
🔥 3. SERVICE YOZ
import 'package:android_dynamic_icon/android_dynamic_icon.dart';

class AppIconService {
  static Future<void> changeToBlue() async {
    await AndroidDynamicIcon.setAlternateIconName("MainActivityBlue");
  }

  static Future<void> changeToDark() async {
    await AndroidDynamicIcon.setAlternateIconName("MainActivityDark");
  }
}
🔥 4. UI GA QO‘SH (SENING SCREENDA)

RadioListdan keyin qo‘sh:

const SizedBox(height: 20),
const Text("Ilova belgisi"),

ListTile(
  title: const Text("Ko‘k ikon"),
  onTap: () async {
    await AppIconService.changeToBlue();
  },
),

ListTile(
  title: const Text("Qora ikon"),
  onTap: () async {
    await AppIconService.changeToDark();
  },
),
